Benico Enterprise Projects
by Bethan Nicole Douglas

JOB HUNTING: I am currently looking for new employment, ideally in office work.
I have worked Admininstration, I.T. & Accounts for Solicitors in the past but I'm a quick learner and open to new opportunities. View my CV.

I switched from Office work after 20 years into the Food Retail Sector, working initially in the Warehouse at Marks and Spencer, I transferred to the Food Hall, where I have been for 9 years.

I am now looking to further develop my career and find employment where I can feel that I can give consideration to moving into at least a middle management position at some point in the future, which I don't not feel is right for me in my current employment.

Whilst I have not had any recent office experience, I have still kept up computer skills with personal office suite projects. I have also assisted my current employers when such skills were required. I produced a store newsletter and posters for more than a year and have done this for my previous employers too.

I always aim for high accuracy and efficiency in everything I do, whether working on my own or as part of a team. I have always been punctual with a low absence record, a copy of which I can provide if requested.

(RELAUNCHED 2019)
WEBSITE SERVICES: There are many free web design services available, if you have the time to work on them yourself, however, if you would like someone else to take the strain and set everything up for you, to include domain name(s), hosting, design and emails, then please get in touch.
Prices from £50, for a 1 page, hosted and maintained site, with 1 or 2 email accounts. Annual renewal prices may be lower as some costs are a one-off charge.

(RELAUNCHED 2019 - for Personal Finances or Small Businesses)
ACCOUNTING SERVICES: I have in the past provided accounting services for sole traders and with a good range of new software available I am available again to take on new contracts. 
Small Businesses: Services can include Income, Expenditure balance sheets, payroll, creditors, setting up integrated accounting packages. £15 per hour.
Personal Finances: To include Bank Transactions, Pensions, Debts and financial budget plans. Services from £20 one off fee.
If you may be interested then please use the Online Chat service to tell me a bit about your requirements and I'll see how I can help. 

CARAVAN PAGES: Since 2012, I have been providing Help and Advice for Caravan Owners and Guests. Free to use Booking Forms, Terms & Conditions, General Advice, Welcome Pack, other information and advice for Caravan Owners as well as an Advice Pack for Guests.
1 Page web sites are available for owners, from £40, depending on requirements.

LOTTERY SYNDICATE: Launched in 2015. Open to UK residents aged 16+ for just £5 a month. Entries to ALL standard EuroMillions and Lotto draws, and other draws when funds permit. More members will result in more chances of prizes as more draws can be entered. Why not get your work team to join to save you having to manage a syndicate yourself. 
COMPUTER SUPPORT: If your Windows computer is feeling a little under the weather then, if you are relatively local, then I don't mind seeing if I can help out. I can even help re-install Windows, or install a secondary operating system, such as Linux Mint, which is perfect if all you need is Internet and an Office Suite. If you wish to try this installation yourself then follow my Linux Mint Quick Guide.

A few of my recommendations

Linux Mint for dual running with Windows 10, Starling Bank a fully mobile UK bank, with Euro account, top-up savings and debit card receipts, Revolut ideal for foreign exchange and can even accept debit card payments. Safe and spam free: That's Nonsense, Facecrooks and Hoax-Slayer

01. About

Adacity Media is a digital advertising agency working with clients across the globe. With years of experience in the digital media space we understand the unique challenges faced by product owners and service providers. We offer fully managed, performance-based campaigns across all devices and screen sizes. We also offer a full spectrum of ad types to best suit your business including native, interstitial, pop up/under and simple text.

We pride ourselves on delivering superior LTV to our clients. We look forward to working with you no matter how big or small your business goals are.





02.Our Process

The most important aspect of any campaign - unique angles and targeting

0.1Creative Ideas

We press the on button and begin driving targeted traffic, collecting and quantifying data, translating raw numbers into something meaningful.

0.2Deployment

We begin optimising both inventory sources and LPs in real-time to deliver highly targeted LTV leads for your business.

0.3Optimisation

We now go deeper with our targeting, repeating steps 2 and 3, to generate more traffic and more leads. How far we go is up to you!

0.4Scale

03. Why Us





Deep Inventory Access

We have access to multiple inventory sources which translates into more customers for your business.

Proprietary Tracking

Our proprietary tracking system sits on dedicated load-balanced servers. This ensures latency fidelity no matter how far you scale.

Intelligent Optimisation

We utilise A/B testing to find out what works and what doesn't to produce higher conversion rates.

Performance Model

Our business model means that we take all the risk upfront and only get paid once a qualified lead has been delivered to you. In short, if we don't perform, you don't pay.

Superior LTV

We ensure that leads are qualified to your exact specifications resulting in higher quality and therefore higher customer LTV.

In-Depth Analytics

We collect and quantify a multitude of data points such as CTR, EPC, bounce rate, conversion rate, all of which can be leveraged to produce super targeted, highly converting campaigns.

05.Contact Us







Get in Touch


Don't hesitate to get in touch with us. If you feel like we could be a good fit for your business let's talk.

  • Phone: +44 7766713930
  • Email: enquiries1@adacitymedia.com



Thanks for getting in touch! We will get back to you shortly.
